<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>8192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>12221</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆和约翰在树林里远足。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们是很好的朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们已经是很多年的好朋友了。”汤姆说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊。”约翰同意说，“我们从小就是好朋友了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆很幸运，因为他在自己的农场里找到了金子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他变得很富有。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是约翰很贫穷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆一家住在大豪宅里，但是约翰一家住在小木屋里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“约翰，我觉得你家人需要一间大房子。”汤姆说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，我们当然需要，但是我们太穷了。”约翰说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请让我为你们建造一间大房子吧。”汤姆提议道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很幸运，我想把这好运气也分享给你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你，汤姆。”约翰说，“你真的是一个好朋友。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85757</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>约翰和汤姆愉快地穿过了森林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85758</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他们看到一只熊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>熊也看到了他们，并向他们跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97866</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>约翰跑得很快。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把汤姆丢在后面，以最快的速度跑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他爬上了一棵树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆跑得不如熊快。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115406</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他转过身去，看到熊正在逼近。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没用了。我完了。熊要吃掉我了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，汤姆有了一个主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“熊不吃死人。”他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是汤姆躺在地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他屏住了呼吸，躺在地上一动也不动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>熊闻了闻汤姆，但是汤姆一动也不动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>熊仔细地看着汤姆，舔了舔他的耳朵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154949</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆还是一动也不动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154950</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢，请不要吃我，不要吃我！”汤姆想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165591</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，熊走开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>约翰看到熊走了之后，从树上爬了下来，跑向汤姆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那头熊没有吃你。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是啊，他没吃我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186145</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>约翰很惊讶。汤姆看起来并不开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186146</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“汤姆，你应该开心啊，你还活着！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也这么觉得。”汤姆说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194731</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>约翰不明白为什么汤姆这么不开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“熊对他说了什么？”他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“汤姆，熊对你说什么了？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“熊说：‘你的朋友跑走了。他不是一个好朋友。’”汤姆回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>约翰意识到他没有做到一个真正的朋友应该做的事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225741</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆悲伤地走了，约翰又悲伤又羞愧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231809</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他失去了他的朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>记住，一个真正的朋友永远都会帮助你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>